---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service - Wealth Management" description="Terms of service governing the use of our wealth management services and website.">
  <Navigation />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 via-slate-800 to-navy-900 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-72 h-72 bg-gold-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Terms and conditions governing our wealth management services and client relationships.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <Section 
    title=""
    subtitle=""
    className="py-20 bg-white"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg prose-slate">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-center mb-0">
          <strong>Last Updated:</strong> September 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        By accessing and using this website and our wealth management services, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by the above, please do not use this service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We provide comprehensive wealth management services including but not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
              <li>Investment advisory services</li>
              <li>Financial planning and consultation</li>
              <li>Portfolio management</li>
              <li>Retirement planning</li>
              <li>Estate planning guidance</li>
              <li>Tax optimization strategies</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">3. Client Responsibilities</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        As a client, you agree to:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Provide accurate and complete information about your financial situation</li>
        <li>• Notify us promptly of any material changes in your circumstances</li>
        <li>• Follow our recommendations in good faith</li>
        <li>• Pay all fees and charges as agreed upon</li>
        <li>• Comply with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">4. Investment Advisory Services</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our investment advisory services are provided in accordance with applicable securities laws and regulations. We will:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Act in your best interests as a fiduciary</li>
        <li>• Provide suitable investment recommendations based on your objectives</li>
        <li>• Disclose all material conflicts of interest</li>
        <li>• Maintain appropriate records of all transactions</li>
        <li>• Provide regular account statements and performance reports</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">5. Fees and Compensation</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our fee structure will be disclosed in your investment advisory agreement. Fees may include:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>• Management fees based on assets under management</li>
        <li>• Transaction fees for certain investment products</li>
        <li>• Consultation fees for financial planning services</li>
        <li>• Third-party custodian and administrative fees</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        All fees will be clearly disclosed before services are provided and will be detailed in your client agreement.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">6. Risk Disclosure</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Investing involves risk, including the potential loss of principal. Past performance does not guarantee future results. You should consider the following risks:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Market risk - investments may lose value due to market conditions</li>
        <li>• Credit risk - issuers may default on their obligations</li>
        <li>• Liquidity risk - investments may be difficult to sell</li>
        <li>• Inflation risk - purchasing power may decrease over time</li>
        <li>• Concentration risk - over-concentration in specific sectors or securities</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">7. Confidentiality and Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We maintain strict confidentiality regarding your personal and financial information. Our privacy practices are detailed in our Privacy Policy, which complies with applicable privacy laws including GDPR 2025 and North American privacy regulations.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We will not disclose your information to third parties except as required by law or as necessary to provide our services.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, our liability for any claims arising from our services shall be limited to the amount of fees paid by you for the specific service giving rise to the claim. We shall not be liable for:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
        <li>• Loss of profits or investment opportunities</li>
        <li>• Market fluctuations or economic conditions beyond our control</li>
        <li>• Third-party actions or omissions</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">9. Termination</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Either party may terminate this agreement with written notice. Upon termination:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• All outstanding fees must be paid</li>
        <li>• We will provide final account statements</li>
        <li>• Confidentiality obligations continue indefinitely</li>
        <li>• You may transfer your accounts to another advisor</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">10. Regulatory Compliance</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We are committed to compliance with all applicable laws and regulations, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-2">
        <li>• Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) regulations</li>
        <li>• Financial Industry Regulatory Authority (FINRA) rules</li>
        <li>• State securities laws</li>
        <li>• Anti-money laundering (AML) requirements</li>
        <li>• Know Your Customer (KYC) obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">11. Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Any disputes arising from these terms or our services shall be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with the rules of the American Arbitration Association. The arbitration shall be conducted in the jurisdiction where our principal office is located.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">12. Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the state where our principal office is located, without regard to conflict of law principles.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">13. Modifications</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Material changes will be communicated to clients with at least 30 days' notice. Continued use of our services after such modifications constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-6">14. Contact Information</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> legal@wealthmanagement.com</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-2"><strong>Phone:</strong> (555) 123-4567</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600"><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Financial District, Suite 100, New York, NY 10004</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 text-center">
          This Terms of Service is effective as of September 2025 and applies to all users of this website and our services.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
